References: jsc#PED-9898 jsc#PED-10191 jsc#PED-10197 jsc#PED-10226 jsc#PED-10237 jsc#PED-10340 jsc#PED-10852 jsc#PED-11022 CVE-2024-49893 bsc#1232350

[WHAT & HOW]
dc_state_get_stream_status can return null, and therefore null must be
checked before stream_status is used.

This fixes 1 NULL_RETURNS issue reported by Coverity.

